metadata.name: Miss Metaverse
metadata.description:
// It's time to swim in Metaverse space // We have overcome gravity and raised our pixel walls // Our evolution tubes are fed // All calculations create an emotional number // Miss Metaverse will decide reality // New avatars, broken hearts and gluttonous crabs // 

It is the second piece of the Subvision Series.

Digital Artwork
5906 x 5906px 300 dpi 

2022 - Bulent Gultek
